NQ Scalper (EMA Trend + Pullback Reclaim) [v5] is a fast intraday strategy built for 1–5 minute charts. It trades pullbacks in the direction of trend using a 100 EMA trend filter and a fast EMA reclaim trigger. RSI confirmation helps filter weak setups, and an optional VWAP filter can further align entries with intraday bias.

The strategy uses ATR-based stop loss and take profit, with an optional trailing stop. Designed primarily for NQ/MNQ scalping during regular market hours. Best used for backtesting, optimization, and forward testing with proper risk management.
